We can use ServiceNow’s workflow to send multi-party notifications where needed, but eliminate notifications that merely create pointless work. Regarding localization: in 3E the Australia and UK payee requests are handled; globally, payee requests come through the US instance. The work and updates can be done through 3E’s workflow table.

