If vendor intake is built into the new P2P workflow that would make things easier. The ARAX report is scheduled and someone tells AP to run it. That scheduled email is the request to the banking portal, and it runs weekly — typically every Friday — as a calendar event. We track that weekly in our team calendar: check the report, update bank details in 3E, and then send them to Chair? (I think "Chair" or a team called "ShareWell" was mentioned).

